2:T710,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Lokalise better than Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Lokalise scores 8.0 overall while Unbabel scores 7.0. Lokalise is best for development teams and mobile apps, while Unbabel excels for customer support teams and global companies."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Lokalise or Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Lokalise starts at Free and Unbabel starts at Custom. Lokalise offers a free plan.  Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Lokalise to Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Lokalise and Unbabel support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Lokalise vs Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Lokalise holds an overall rating of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10. Unbabel has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 7/10. Users praise Lokalise for excellent developer workflow integration and Unbabel for human-quality translation at scale."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Lokalise or Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Lokalise for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Unbabel remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize human-quality translation at scale. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"cla